						<h2><a href="https://lithub.com/can-zohran-mamdani-survive-at-the-intersection-of-identity-politics-and-democratic-socialism/" title="Can Zohran Mamdani Survive at the Intersection of Identity Politics and Democratic Socialism?">Can Zohran Mamdani Survive at the Intersection of Identity Politics and Democratic Socialism?</a></h2>
